|--------|-----------|------------|
| artistDashboard | Artist Dashboard | 1 |
| artistFileBrowser | File Browser | 2 |
| artistProjectManagement | Project Management | - |
| artistTimeClock | Time Clock | - |
| artistLogging | Activity Log | 90 |
