## 5. DATABASE SCHEMA (Database: `simeckdb`)

### Table: `artists`
| Column | Type | Purpose |
|--------|------|---------|
| username | varchar(50) | Login name |
| firstname / lastname | varchar(50) | Legal name |
| nickname | varchar(50) | Display nickname |
| password | varchar(500) | Bcrypt hash |
| userID | int (PK, AUTO_INCREMENT) | Internal ID |
| active | int(1) | Active flag |
| role | varchar(10) | `admin` or `artist` |
| project_assignments | varchar(100) | Comma-separated PIDs (e.g. `C01,P01,C05`) |
| theme | varchar(20) | Theme ID (default `dark-boo`) |
| timezone | varchar(40) | e.g. `America/Phoenix` |
| availability | varchar(120) | 7-element pipe-separated 48-bit ints (`0|0|0|0|0|0|0`) |
| availability_this_week | varchar(50) | Same format, overrides base during current week |
| log_rows_per_page | int | Pagination preference for log viewer |
| phone_country_code | int | Country code for SMS (default 1) |
| phone_number | int | Phone number |
| receive_texts | int(1) | SMS opt-in flag |

### Table: `clients`
| Column | Type | Purpose |
|--------|------|---------|
| username | varchar(70) | Login name (can be email) |
| firstname / lastname | varchar(50) | Legal name |
| password | varchar(500) | Bcrypt hash |
| project_assignments | varchar(100) | Comma-separated PIDs |
| active | int(1) | Active flag |
| outstandingBalance | decimal(20,2) | Balance tracking |
| point_of_contact | varchar(20) | Artist username who is POC |
| theme | varchar(20) | Theme ID |
| lock_overrides | int | Number of available lock overrides |
| timezone | varchar(40) | Client's timezone |
| availability | varchar(120) | 7-element bitmask (same format as artists) |
| phone_country_code | varchar(20) | Country code for SMS |
| phone_number | int | Phone number |
| receive_texts | int(1) | SMS opt-in flag |

### Table: `projects`
| Column | Type | Purpose |
|--------|------|---------|
| pid | varchar(5) | Project ID (e.g. `C01`, `P00`, `P01`) — `C` = client, `P` = internal |
| project_name | varchar(50) | Display name |
| active | int(1) | Active flag (inactive = zipped) |
| active_path | varchar(200) | Filesystem path relative to root (e.g. `/files/Projects/clientProjects/C01_SetSail`) |
| inactive_zip_path | varchar(200) | Path to zip archive |
| transitioning | int(1) | Set to 1 during archive/unarchive (background process) |
| type | varchar(10) | `internal` or `client` |
| description | varchar(500) | Short description |
| leader | varchar(50) | Project lead's username |
| size_on_disk | int | Cached folder size in bytes |

### Table: `timeclockshifts`
| Column | Type | Purpose |
|--------|------|---------|
| user | varchar(50) | Artist username |
| shift_id | int (PK, AUTO_INCREMENT) | Shift ID |
| time_in | datetime | Clock-in time (stored in America/Phoenix) |
| time_out | datetime | Clock-out time (nullable = still active) |

### Table: `logs`
| Column | Type | Purpose |
|--------|------|---------|
| username | varchar(50) | Acting user |
| time | datetime | Timestamp |
| user_action | varchar(500) | Action description |
| ip_address | varchar(20) | Client IP |
| extra_data | varchar(500) | Details |
| project_target | varchar(10) | Affected project PID or `System` |
| impersonated_by | varchar(50) | Null unless action was done while impersonating |

### Table: `filecomments`
| Column | Type | Purpose |
|--------|------|---------|
| owner | varchar(50) | Comment author's username |
| comment_time | datetime | When it was posted |
| parent_file_url | varchar(300) | URL-encoded file/folder path |
| comment_order | int | Order within same parent |
| comment_content | longtext | The comment text |

### Table: `lockedfiles`
| Column | Type | Purpose |
|--------|------|---------|
| lockid | int (PK, AUTO_INCREMENT) | Lock ID |
| filepath | varchar(300) | Root-relative file path |
| locktime | datetime | When locked |
| assetlock | int(1) | Lock editing of the file (default 1) |
| commentlock | int(1) | Lock commenting on the file (default 1) |

### Table: `artistdocuments` / `clientdocuments`
Secure document delivery system (separate from elFinder). Used for contracts, tax forms, etc.
| Column | Type | Purpose |
|--------|------|---------|
| owner | varchar(30/70) | Owner's username |
| uploadID | int (PK, AUTO_INCREMENT) | Document ID |
| filepath | varchar(200) | Server file path |
| uploaded_by | varchar(20) | Who uploaded it |
| upload_time | datetime | When uploaded |

### Table: `daysoff`
| Column | Type | Purpose |
|--------|------|---------|
| id | int (PK, AUTO_INCREMENT) | Record ID |
| username | varchar(50) | Artist username |
| date_off_start | date | Start date |
| date_off_end | date | End date (nullable = single day) |
| start_time | time | Start time of time-off block (nullable = all day) |
| end_time | time | End time of time-off block (nullable = all day) |

